## Org Summary (`/api/ai/summarize-org`)

Aggregates all employee scores then sends compact stats to Gemini (no raw report content):

- Org average score
- Score distribution bands (8–10 strong, 6–7.9 good, 4–5.9 average, 0–3.9 needs improvement)
- Department breakdown (avg score per dept)
- Top 3 and bottom 3 criteria by average score

Returns:

```json
{
  "headline": "One sentence org performance tone",
  "overall_rating": "good",
  "highlights": ["strength 1", "strength 2"],
  "concerns": ["risk or gap"],
  "trend": "stable",
  "recommendation": "1–2 sentence strategic recommendation"
}
```

`overall_rating`: `strong | good | average | needs_improvement`
`trend`: `improving | stable | declining | insufficient_data`

