## Model Config

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| Model | `gemini-2.5-flash` |
| Temperature (scoring) | `0.1` |
| Temperature (org summary) | `0.4` |
| Max tokens (scoring) | `8192` |
| Max tokens (consistency check) | `300` |
| Response format | `application/json` (forced) |
| Retry logic | `withRetry` wrapper handles 429s |
